	<h1 class="title">很久没演爱情片的刘青云说，他在《三城记》里找到一点香港的味道</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4369/small/4369.jpg?1419239008" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">晏文静 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-02 17:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/14273/medium/14273.jpg?1441091380" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


